@startuml
title Viaverse Media Asset — State Diagram

[*] --> PENDING_UPLOAD
PENDING_UPLOAD --> UPLOADED : confirm upload
UPLOADED --> PROCESSING : enqueue
PROCESSING --> PENDING_MODERATION : derivatives ready
PENDING_MODERATION --> APPROVED : safe
PENDING_MODERATION --> MANUAL_REVIEW : uncertain
MANUAL_REVIEW --> APPROVED : admin approves
MANUAL_REVIEW --> REJECTED : admin rejects
PENDING_MODERATION --> REJECTED : unsafe
APPROVED --> ATTACHED : attach to context
APPROVED --> DELETED : owner/admin delete
REJECTED --> DELETED : cleanup

ATTACHED --> [*]
DELETED --> [*]

note bottom
Only APPROVED media can become visible in public/profile/search surfaces.
Chat/job private media can still require per-context authorization.
end note
@enduml
